I have undone information removed that states my job title and the fact that I am an author. My authorship is proven elsewhere in the article, and I have held the same job for 12 years. I claim the moral right to credit for my work.

Added a parenthetical remark to explain what "Lusophony" means.
/* History */ Corrected the impression that I was THE director of GDC, or its leader. I was A director, not THE director.
